<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
  <title>UserHub Secure — Hardened community platform</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="navbar">
    <div class="navbar-inner">
      <a href="/" class="brand">
        <span class="brand-mark">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
        </span>
        <span>UserHub</span>
        <span class="brand-secure-badge">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
          Hardened
        </span>
      </a>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <% if (user) { %>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/profile">Profile</a>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/users">Members</a>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/logout">Logout</a>
        <% } else { %>
          <a class="nav-link" href="/login">Login</a>
          <a class="nav-link active" href="/signup">Sign up</a>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="container">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-tag">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        Secure build · v2.0
      </div>
      <h1>UserHub, hardened from the ground up.</h1>
      <p>The same community platform — now with parameterised queries, bcrypt password hashing, JWT auth, strict CSP, structured logging, and rate-limited endpoints.</p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <% if (user) { %>
          <a href="/profile" class="btn btn-light">Go to your profile</a>
          <a href="/users" class="btn btn-ghost">Browse members</a>
        <% } else { %>
          <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-light">Create your account</a>
          <a href="/login" class="btn btn-ghost">I already have one</a>
        <% } %>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"/><path d="M21 12c0 1.66-4 3-9 3s-9-1.34-9-3"/><path d="M3 5v14c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Parameterised SQL</h3>
        <p>Every database query uses prepared statements. The <code>admin' OR '1'='1</code> bypass simply does not work.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>bcrypt + JWT auth</h3>
        <p>Passwords are bcrypt-hashed (cost 12). Sessions are signed JWTs in an HttpOnly, SameSite=Strict cookie.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><polyline points="2 17 12 22 22 17"/><polyline points="2 12 12 17 22 12"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Helmet headers + CSP</h3>
        <p>Strict Content-Security-Policy, HSTS, X-Frame-Options, no <code>X-Powered-By</code> leak.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Rate limiting</h3>
        <p>Auth endpoints capped at 20 requests / 15 min per IP — brute force becomes impractical.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Structured logging</h3>
        <p>winston writes JSON-line events to <code>security.log</code> — every login, failure, and rejected token is auditable.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-check"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Input validation</h3>
        <p>Every signup field is validated server-side. Weak passwords and bad emails never reach the database.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <% if (user) { %>
      <div class="card">
        <h2>Welcome back, <%= user.username %>!</h2>
        <p class="card-sub">Your session is signed and HttpOnly. You're good to go.</p>
        <a href="/profile" class="btn btn-primary">Open your profile</a>
      </div>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
